      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road! I've made sure to keep up with it so it's ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a smooth ride at a great price, come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
