    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system for exceptional throttle response across the rev range. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring a proactive subframe reinforcement kit to address common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-intended kinematics with refreshed bushings and MacPherson front/multi-link rear geometry. Recent mechanical overhaul includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. This example is mechanically robust, presenting with the communicative steering and balanced weight distribution synonymous with the M-division\u2019s golden era.",
